But ultimately, Radyo Veritas' key role is not political but spiritual.

The "Voice of Asian Christianity's" two-fold objectives - evangelization and human development, are the guiding principles with which it reaches out to the millions of Filipinos that tune into them. And this is reflected in the Radyo station's programming.

Its Radyo programs touch on matters of Christian faith - dialogue with religions and cultures, catechesis, the role of the church in the modern world, doctrine, Liturgy, Sacraments, etc.

For its developmental features, Radyo Veritas Asia broadcasts programs on health, community development, science and technology, women and youth, the family, folklore, history, and other related features.
